	<font class="Body1" size="-1">
	<ul>
		<li>You must be at least level 40(See below for Exceptions).</li>
		<li>You must send an email to all <a
		href="mailto:eqaddicts@earthlink.net;Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com;Innoruukcom@hotmail.com;czarra@home.com;Javen_Starblaze@hotmail.com?Subject=Application to The 
		Hidden">Officers</a> with the following information:
			<ul>
				<li>Why you want to join.</li>
				<li>Why you would be a good addition to The Hidden.</li>
				<li>Your Character(s) name, level, race, class,	and usual playing time.</li>
				<li>What previous guilds you have been in, why you left or why you want to leave for The
				Hidden.</li>
				<li>If you have previously been in The Hidden and would like to rejoin please also
				include how you have changed and why you should be let back in.</li>
			</ul>
		This application will be posted in the Applications forum where only Members have access.</li>
		<li>Next a current Member of The Hidden must sponsor you by posting in the thread created when
		your application was recieved. A Member should only sponsor a Prospective
		Member if they feel they would be a good addition to the guild. This means the
		sponsor should know the Prospective Member and have grouped with them before.</li>
		<li>All Members have one week from the time a Prospective Member is sponsored to vote.
			<ul>
				<li>If two or more members vote no, your admission to The Hidden is denied.</li>
				<li>If after one week of voting 50% of all active members have not voted for you voting
				will be extended another week.</li>
				<li>If after four weeks you do not have 50% of all active members votes your application
				will be denied.</li>
				<li>For those wishing to join below the level 40 minimum. You may be
				sponsored by a Member and if all votes are for you and the Council
				agrees you may join.</li>
				<li>A Prospective Member may apply as many times as they wish in the
				case that they are denied membership on prior applications.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Once voting has taken place you shall be invited to the guild as soon as you
		can meet up with an Officer.</li>
		<li>All twinks and secondary characters are welcome regardless of level.</li>
		<li>You will recieve access to the Members Only section after providing your EZBoard username and
		are considered a full Member, and as a Member will follow the <a href="rules.asp">rules</a>
		governing Members.</li>
	</ul>
	Best of luck to all prospective members.<br><br>
